Open the bread and remove two slices, laying them side by side.
Open peanut butter jar
Remove some peanut butter with the knife
Spread the peanut butter onto the bread until you have as much as you want, removing more from the jar as needed.
Open jelly jar.
Remove a table spoonful of jelly.
Spread the jelly on the bread until you have as much as you want, removing more from the jar as needed.
Place the two slices together, peanut butter and jelly facing inwards, press down slightly, and enjoy
